Jean Kemm https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Kemm 0 Jean Kemm (15 May 1874–1939) was a French stage and theater actor and film director. Kemm was born Jules Adolphe Félix Bécheret in the 2nd arrondissement of Paris and died in Paris in 1939. Jean_Kemm ( 15_May_1874 – 1939 ) was a_French_stage_and_theater_actor_and_film_director .
